If I was a bad boy I would travel the world meeting people to have grand experiences with, having sex everywhere we went. In every country. 

If I was a bad boy I would find a crazy adventure and a partner to do it and go try it out. Wing suit flying. Mountain biking. Cliff jumping. Climbing a mountain. Hot Springs. You name it. 

If I was bad I would become super rich and spend all of my money on food, cars, and comfort. I would eat the best foods from around the world. I would try that best drinks. I would sleep in the best hotels. I would be pampered in the best ways.
